## Build Order

1. **`src/config.py`** — Model names + classifier settings from `.env`
2. **`src/agents/document_classifier.py`** — Classifier agent (small model, 4 categories)
3. **Keep `process_listing.py` as Stage 1 converter** — outputs markdown + consolidated markdown only.
4. **Add `src/pipeline/classify_and_bucket.py`** — classifies each file, rebuilds `buckets/` on rerun, and writes `doc_manifest.json`.
5. **Modify [run_modular_pipeline.py](file:///Users/aryanjain/Documents/OZL/oz-doc-processor/run_modular_pipeline.py)** — remove fallback mode, require manifest, read from bucketed markdown and add `--stage extract` + `--agent`.
6. **Modify `orchestrate_pipeline.py`** — add stage flags (`convert`, `classify`, `extract`, `all`) and stage guards.
7. **Test on TierraMark** — Most diverse file set, ideal validation for rerun and bucket rebuild behavior.
